    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "If you live in Thailand, you can easily find Thai alphabet writing practice books which have pictures showing the meaning of these consonant names to help you create connections between consonant names and the meaning of these names. Use them as writing playgrounds and practise to perfect your Thai characters. Such books are sold everywhere, usually with a BIG picture of a chicken (which is the first letter of the alphabet) on the cover. It's worth it—get one."
